title: Lord of the Fallen Hands-On Preview
description:
After playing roughly two hours of Lords of the Fallen for preview, it's clear developer Hexworks has a better understanding of what makes a good Souls-like click this time around.

title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles The Last Ronin Official Teaser Trailer
description:
A brand new Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles game has been teased today during THQ Nordiq's Summer Showcase from Black Forest Games. Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles The Last Ronin is currently in development.

#tmnt #thqnordic #gaming

title: Mortal Kombat 1 Smoke vs Li Mei High Level Gameplay
description:
During the latest Kombat Kast for Mortal Kombat 1 we got to watch a high level developer match with Li Mei using the Frost kameo against Smoke using the Sektor kameo. We even got to see a throw back to an old Mortal Kombat 3 finisher at the end of the match!

#mortalkombat #mk1 #gaming

title: Mortal Kombat 1 Smoke, Ashrah, and Geras Gameplay Breakdown
description:
Join the Kombat Kast Tyler, Derek, and Stephanie as they go over Smoke, Ashrah, and Geras moves in Mortal Kombat 1. Check out the timestamps below for each character with their kameo. We even get to see each of their fatal blows!

Timestamps
0:00 Intro
0:25 Smoke with Sub Zero Kameo
7:35 Smoke Fatal Blow
9:47 Ashrah with Frost Kameo
16:50 Ashrah Fatal Blow
19:52 Geras with Goro Kameo
30:55 Geras Fatal Blow

#mortalkombat #mk1 #gaming
